eas_text: A CIVIL AUTHORITY HAS ISSUED A REQUIRED MONTHLY TEST FOR THE FOLLOWING COUNTIES/AREAS: San Juan; Skagit; Whatcom, WA; AT 06:49 AM ON SEP 10, 2025 EFFECTIVE UNTIL 09:49 AM. MESSAGE FROM WSLF/CAP.
extra_text: This is the Skagit County Department of Emergency Management conducting a test of the Emergency Alert System. In the event of an emergency this system would bring you important information. The following tones will conclude this test.
